CPQ Quote Intelligence Agent
A Chrome extension that analyzes Salesforce CPQ quotes in real time using Claude AI. When a sales rep is on a CPQ Quote record, they click the extension icon and get a sidebar showing configuration flags, a discount recommendation, and a copyable approval justification — without leaving the page and without any changes to the Salesforce org.

________________________________________
Architecture
Chrome Extension (content.js + background.js)
        ↓
Salesforce REST API (as the logged-in rep)
        ↓
Node.js Backend (Express)
        ↓
Anthropic Claude API
The extension reads the quote directly using the rep's active session. The backend holds the Anthropic API key — it is never exposed to the browser.

________________________________________
What It Does
•	Configuration Flags — reviews quote lines against active product rules, checks for missing bundle components, quantity anomalies, expired dates, and discount policy violations
•	Discount Recommendation — suggests a recommended discount with floor and ceiling, based on quote total, account industry, and existing discount schedules
•	Approval Justification — generates a ready-to-copy approval note structured for deal desk review

