Supported Salesforce URL Formats
The extension activates on the following domains:
•	*.salesforce.com
•	*.force.com
•	*.lightning.force.com
•	*.trailblaze.lightning.force.com
•	*.my.salesforce.com
•	*.trailblaze.my.salesforce.com

________________________________________
Known Limitations
•	Works only on individual Quote record pages, not list views
•	Requires the rep to be actively logged into Salesforce in Chrome
•	Product Rules and Discount Schedules are fetched with a limit of 50 records each, large orgs with extensive CPQ configuration may need this increased
•	Each analysis consumes approximately 3 Anthropic API calls

